Hi everyone, my first extra goal as Cypress on-call is now complete! I made a doc of all our Cypress utils:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yljt2UCqqC23peqFCWOUSVyn0EXxoM9gc-AjeermSZw
I included a rudimentary tags column so that it's easier to search for a util that you might need. I hope you find it useful!
